---
title: Saucy Beyond Meat® Ragù with Olive Tapenade
description: This twist on classic spaghetti Bolognese is a winner! Penne replaces spaghetti, and the ragù is packed with tender Beyond Meat® and tons of flavour. Topped with fresh olive tapenade, this dish will have everyone coming back for seconds!
